别指着那个。他有心脏病。

936
00:45:53,710 --> 00:45:55,678
Shut up! Oh, my God!
闭嘴！哦，我的天！

937
00:45:55,712 --> 00:45:57,447
Fuck. Come on!
操。快点！

938
00:45:57,480 --> 00:45:59,282
He's having a heart attack. No, no, no, lady.
他心脏病发作了。不，不，不，女士。

939
00:45:59,315 --> 00:46:00,783
Get up and give me the money now.
起来把钱给我，现在。

940
00:46:00,817 --> 00:46:03,052
Shit, come on! Oh!
该死，快点！哦！

941
00:46:05,388 --> 00:46:07,123
Stop it.
住手。

942
00:46:07,156 --> 00:46:08,358
Calm down.
冷静下来。

943
00:46:20,036 --> 00:46:21,804
Mm. Feel better?
嗯。感觉好点了吗？

944
00:46:21,838 --> 00:46:23,706
Yeah.
是的。

945
00:46:24,941 --> 00:46:26,781
You are gonna take this couple to the hospital.
你要把这对夫妇送到医院。

946
00:46:26,809 --> 00:46:28,378
And no more stealing.
别再偷东西了。

947
00:46:28,411 --> 00:46:29,846
The bite was from your cat.
咬伤是你的猫造成的。

948
00:46:29,879 --> 00:46:32,281
You guys, take CPR courses.
你们，去上CPR课程。

949
00:46:32,315 --> 00:46:34,884
You hate junk food.
你讨厌垃圾食品。

950
00:46:34,917 --> 00:46:36,753
And get "Public Enemy."
去买《人民公敌》。

951
00:46:36,786 --> 00:46:38,855
The Cagney one.
卡格尼演的那部。

952
00:46:40,790 --> 00:46:42,158
You all right?
你还好吗？

953
00:46:43,292 --> 00:46:45,762
I could hypnotize you,
我可以催眠你，

954
00:46:45,795 --> 00:46:49,832
but I've been wanting to tell you.
但我一直想告诉你。

955
00:46:49,866 --> 00:46:51,076
So what are you saying? You broke up with me 'cause
所以你是说？你跟我分手是因为

956
00:46:51,100 --> 00:46:53,445
you wouldn't drink my blood? Is that what you're telling me?
你不想喝我的血？你是在告诉我这个吗？

957
00:46:53,469 --> 00:46:56,139
I don't drink human blood.
我不喝人血。

958
00:46:56,172 --> 00:46:59,108
You don't? That guy, what was that?
你不喝？那个人，那是什么？

959
00:46:59,142 --> 00:47:02,478
No. Have you ever seen a vampire bat?
不。你见过吸血蝙蝠吗？

960
00:47:04,047 --> 00:47:07,350
A little rodent can get the blood out of an entire cow
一只小啮齿动物能从一整头牛身上吸干血

961
00:47:07,383 --> 00:47:10,286
in a few minutes because of this enzyme in their saliva.
在几分钟内，因为它们唾液中的这种酶。

962
00:47:10,319 --> 00:47:12,789
It's a completely safe blood thinner.
它是一种完全安全的血液稀释剂。

963
00:47:12,822 --> 00:47:14,257
And I also have it.
我也有。

964
00:47:14,290 --> 00:47:16,759
I didn't drink that man's blood.
我没喝那个人的血。

965
00:47:16,793 --> 00:47:19,796
