但我真的得走了。

1018
00:51:02,385 --> 00:51:04,120
What the--
什么——

1019
00:51:10,593 --> 00:51:12,495
Something bothering you? What?
有什么困扰你吗？什么？

1020
00:51:13,663 --> 00:51:14,997
No.
不。

1021
00:51:17,133 --> 00:51:19,435
If there's anything you wanna talk about...
如果你有什么想谈的…

1022
00:51:19,468 --> 00:51:22,171
