你觉得他会告诉他父亲吗？

1027
00:51:34,050 --> 00:51:36,052
No, he wouldn't do that. What about Danny?
不，他不会那么做。那丹尼呢？

1028
00:51:36,085 --> 00:51:37,329
Do you think he'll tell the authorities?
你觉得他会告诉当局吗？

1029
00:51:37,353 --> 00:51:39,488
He'd never. How do you know?
他绝不会。你怎么知道？

1030
00:51:39,522 --> 00:51:41,023
Danny hates authority.
丹尼讨厌权威。

1031
00:51:41,057 --> 00:51:43,057
I'm gonna go to his class so he has to confront me.
我要去他的课上，这样他就必须面对我。

1032
00:51:45,528 --> 00:51:47,063
Are you mad at me?
你生我的气了吗？

1033
00:51:48,464 --> 00:51:50,132
Don't go away. Huh? What?
别走开。嗯？什么？

1034
00:51:54,136 --> 00:51:56,105
Really? Yeah.
真的吗？是的。

1035
00:51:57,173 --> 00:51:59,175
How do you like them apples?
你觉得这些苹果怎么样？

1036
00:51:59,208 --> 00:52:01,243
Garlic?
大蒜？

1037
00:52:01,277 --> 00:52:02,454
You were afraid of it the other night.
你那天晚上怕它。

1038
00:52:02,478 --> 00:52:05,014
Yeah, because I've always hated garlic.
是的，因为我一直讨厌大蒜。

1039
00:52:06,682 --> 00:52:08,250
Can we please just talk about this?
我们能请你谈谈这个吗？

1040
00:52:08,284 --> 00:52:11,220
My father tried to warn me. Against what?
我父亲试图警告我。反对什么？

1041
00:52:11,253 --> 00:52:13,489
I have never harmed a human being or a domestic animal
我从未伤害过一个人或一只家畜

1042
00:52:13,522 --> 00:52:15,191
my entire life.
